w numpy arrays pass through NumPy's aggregation functions (sum, mean, std, etc.), can be wrapped as pandas extension arrays for tabular operations, and ultimately can be passed to scipy statistical functions for advanced analysis.\"\n}\nEOF\ncat /workspace/answer.json\n",
